OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry and cloudy, but
OL,6,Falso some bright spells will occur,
OL,7,Fmainly in the afternoon and away from
OL,8,Fthe coast. Winds remain light and
OL,9,Fvariable, breezy along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy and dry overnight with
OL,12,Fsome thicker cloud moving southwards
OL,13,Fand could give some patchy light rain
OL,14,For drizzle over higher ground. A
OL,15,Fcooler night with light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA cloudy and dry day, perhaps
OL,18,Fwith the odd light shower over the
OL,19,Fhills. Mainly light winds, sunny
OL,20,Fspells at times. Temperatures
OL,21,Fgenerally average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
