OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FPredominantly dry through the period,
OL,7,Fperhaps with the odd light shower over
OL,8,Fthe hills. Mainly light winds, sunny
OL,9,Fspells at times. Temperatures
OL,10,Fgenerally average or slightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
